=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 TagFilter => L<Paws::Connect::ControlPlaneTagFilter>




=head2 UserAttributeFilter => L<Paws::Connect::ControlPlaneUserAttributeFilter>

An object that can be used to specify Tag conditions or Hierarchy Group
conditions inside the SearchFilter.

This accepts an C<OR> of C<AND> (List of List) input where:

=over

=item *

The top level list specifies conditions that need to be applied with
C<OR> operator.

=item *

The inner list specifies conditions that need to be applied with C<AND>
operator.

=back

Only one field can be populated. This object canE<rsquo>t be used along
with TagFilter. Request can either contain TagFilter or
UserAttributeFilter if SearchFilter is specified, combination of both
is not supported and such request will throw AccessDeniedException.



